title: THRANDUIL'S FINAL STAND - Third Age Total War Gameplay
description:
Third Age Total War Gameplay - After the the defeat of the border of the woodland realm.  Thranduil has fallen back to his halls.  He has rallied as many troops and they get ready for their final stand.  The orcs have gather more orcs and are one victory away from conquering the Woodland Realm.  Enjoy the Battle :D

Mod Link: http://www.moddb.com/mods/third-age-reforged

Part 1: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gurg1QSGOMQ
